Package it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Product

package it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Product
The it.unipr.barbato.Interface.Product package contains classes and interfaces related to products. This package provides functionality for managing and manipulating product data. It includes classes for defining product attributes, such as name, price, and description, as well as interfaces for implementing product-related operations.
